   <h1>Classic Deviled Egg Recipe</h1> 
   <p>Deviled eggs are easy to make and a perfect use case for you eggs when you need a quick appetizer. The key to the best deviled eggs is to perfectly boil you egg beforehand.</p>
   <p>You can check out my recipe for the <a href="/recipes/hardboiledegg">Percect Hard Boiled Egg</a> in this recipe book.</p>

   <h2>Ingredients</h2>
   <ul>
    <li>Eggs</li>
    <li>Mayonaise</li>
    <li>Dijon Mustard</li>
    <li>Apple Cider Vinegar</li>
    <li>Paprika</li>
    <li>Salt & Pepper</li>
   </ul>
   <h2>Steps</h2>
   <ol>
    <li><a href="/recipes/hardboiledegg">hard boil your eggs</a></li>
    <li>Slice your eggs lengtwise and scoop out the egg yolk to a small bowl</li>
    <li>Add all other ingredients to the yolk, stir until creamy</li>
    <li>Use a small spoon to scoop the mixture back into the egg whites</li>
    <li>Sprinkle a little paprika over the eggs before serving</li>
   </ol>
